dct_description_sm: Map shows electricity transmission line, public road numbers, house numbers, district and Mukim boundary, and town and village boundary. University of Malaya campus is located. Relief shown by 50 meter contours, spot heights, and hachures. "RSO grid." In lower right corner: "Reprinted by the Directorate of National Mapping, Malaysia No. 24-1970."
dct_publisher_sm: Kuala Lumpur : Directorate of National Mapping, 1970.
